us%2C%20we%20have%20usually%20sold%20all%20our%20produce.%20Also%2C%20we%20sell%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260973%2Frajasthan-couple-turmeric-revolution-earns-lakhs-suicides-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20turmeric%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20Rs%20150%20per%20kg%20compared%20to%20Rs%20240%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20local%20market.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20issue%20lowering%20the%20price%20as%20our%20cost%20of%20production%20becomes%20less%20with%20organic%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanchan%20claims%20she%20is%20the%20first%20such%20farmer%20to%20practice%20turmeric%20farming%20in%20this%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLocal%20farmers%20here%20were%20reluctant%20to%20grow%20turmeric%20as%20it%20has%20a%20longer%20growing%20season%20but%20they%20ignored%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20gives%20definitive%20and%20huge%20returns.%20Other%20than%20being%20able%20to%20earn%20double%20income%2C%20it%20gives%20me%20immense%20contentment%20that%20I%20grow%20the%20produce%20organically.%20The%20more%20we%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20chemical%20pesticides%2C%20the%20more%20toxin-free%20food%20will%20be%20there%20for%20our%20kids%20to%20eat%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Kanchan%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756450735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTurmeric-1-1711519971.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D493453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coming%20from%20an%20agricultural%20family%2C%20Kanchan%20Verma%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20took%20up%20farming%20soon%20after%20her%20marriage.%20Along%20with%20growing%20vegetables%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20maize%2C%20the%20BA%20graduate%20tried%20turmeric%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202020.%20The%20decision%20proved%20fruitful%2C%20bringing%20her%20highe