pen%20to%20paying%20a%20modest%20extra%20charge%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221063%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalaneca%20cofounders%20Ramya%20Rao%20and%20Kavea%20R%20Chavali%20dressed%20in%20saris%20from%20their%20shop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68aff98dcfc04e97619c2cf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKavea%20R%20Chavali%20(right)%20cofounded%20Kalaneca%20with%20her%20sister.%3Cp%3EKalaneca%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Kolthoff%2C%20he%20said%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20diversify%20his%20customer%20base%20and%20plans%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20affected%20small%20businesses%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210c8adea-3ecf-4f5c-96e5-fe72610b2345%5C%22%3EFew%20easy%20options%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EManish%20Kapoor%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Growth%20Catalyst%20Group%20and%20a%20former%20FedEx%20and%20Amazon%20logistics%20executive%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Flogistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20couriers%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20the%20only%20fast%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20the%20cost%20per%20package%20is%20higher%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20tough%20choice%20between%20getting%20goods%20to%20customers%20at%20a%20higher%20cost%20or%20not%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapoor%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20small%20businesses%20could%20consider%20pooling%20shipments%20or%20working%20with%20freight%20forwarders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20micro-businesses%2C%20consolidation%20is%20critical%20to%20survival%20post-de%20minimis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sean%20Henry%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Stord%2C%20a%20logistics%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20moving%20to%20US-based%20fulfillment%20could%20lower%20their%20shipping%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20domestic%20parcels%20are%20much%20faster%20and%20cheaper%20than%20international%20parcels%2C%20now%20that