secondary%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20uses%20a%20proprietary%20dataset%20of%203D-scanned%20heads%20to%20design%20new%20models%20with%20different%20characteristics.%20Yves%20Jacquier%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Ubisoft's%20research%20and%20development%20lab%2C%20La%20Forge%2C%20said%20a%20high-resolution%20head%20can%20typically%20take%20a%20week%20to%20create%2C%20but%20FaceShifter%20can%20quickly%20give%20artists%20a%20foundation%20to%20iterate%20on%20and%20free%20up%20their%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20important%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20technology%2C%20you%20have%20something%20believable%20with%20a%20few%20tweaks%20in%20less%20than%20half%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacquier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20also%20helped%20automate%20complex%20tasks%20for%20developers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcandy-crush-office-sweden-king-video-game-developer-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20mobile-gaming%20company%2C%20by%20boosting%20production%20speeds%20and%20improving%20live%20operations%2C%20or%20continuous%20in-game%20updates.%20Luka%20Crnkovic-Friis%2C%20the%20head%20of%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AI%20acts%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bco-pilot%26quot%3B%20for%20King's%20game%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20us%20write%20and%20review%20code%20faster%2C%20run%20playtesting%20at%20scale%2C%20and%20tune%20mechanics%20across%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Crnkovic-Friis%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20King's%20popular%20puzzle%20game%2C%20%26quot%3BCandy%20Crush%20Saga%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20over%2019%2C000%20levels%2C%20Crnkovic-Friis%20said%20his%20team%20uses%20AI%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20CLI%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20Code%2C%20to%20test%20levels%2C%20make%20design%20adjustments%2C%20and%20refine%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Jam%20and%20Tea%20Studios%2C%20AI%20is%20even%20more%20of%20an%20influential%20collaborator%20in%20the%20development%20process.%20The%20early-stage%20studio%20developed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jamandtea.studio%2Fretail-mage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERetail%20Mage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20AI-native%20job-simulation%20game%2C%20with%20LLMs%20to%20create%20more%20dynamic%20interactions%20with%20NPCs%20and%20the%20game's%20environment.%20This%20meant%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20development%20process%20was%20in%20English%2C%20instead%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-ai-silicon-valley-andrej-karpathy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoding%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20made%20production%20accessible%20to%20more%20team%20members%20and%20contributed%20to%20faster%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20had%20that%20technology%20internally%20in%20the%20game%20to%20be%20able%20to%20quickly%20and%20rapidly%20generate%20content%20and%20generate%20dialogue%20and%20generate%20experiences%2C%20our%20iteration%20process%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20skyrocketed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aaron%20Farr%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20of%20Jam%20and%20Tea%20Studios.%20%26quot%3BWe%20built%20Retail%20Mage%20in%20approximately%205%20months%2C%20which%20is%20an%20insane%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retail%20Mage%20AI%20video%20game%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68adc2ea194a2d49b8af2cba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22388%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20%26quot%3BRetail%20Mage%2C%26quot%3B%20players%20can%20help%20customers%20at%20the%20magic%20store%2C%20MageMart%2C%20by%20speaking%20with%20the%20NPCs%20and%20altering%20in-game%20objects%20to%20satisfy%20requests.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Jam%20%26amp%3B%20Tea%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b49bcd31-044d-43a7-b3ff-b93c2f28db4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI-powered%20gameplay%20is%20experimental%20and%20costly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20studios%20are%20already%20using%20machine%20learning%20and%20genAI%20to%20improve%20their%20development%20processes%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20still%20experimenting%20with%20how%20the%20tech%20can%20reshape%20the%20player%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUbisoft%20has%20used%20AI%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubisoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fstudio%2Flaforge%2Fnews%2F6cY2C5m3H5RkFAAsiPYpRh%2Fconfrence-du-cedec-joshua-romoff-explique-comment-crer-des-bots-joueurs-efficaces-grce-au-renforcement-profond%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20smarter%20programming%20for%20NPCs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubisoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fstudio%2Flaforge%2Fnews%2F54QiUaTH5oCX7MUhSSgrGy%2Flarge-language-models-for-toxicity-detection-toxbuster%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoderate%20in-game%20chats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20more%20dynamic%20gameplay%20features%2C%20such%20as%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ubisoft.com%2Fen-us%2Farticle%2F5qXdxhshJBXoanFZApdG3L%2Fhow-ubisofts-new-generative-ai-prototype-changes-the-narrative-for-npcs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENEO%20NPC%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20uses%20LLMs%20for%20spontaneous%20dialogue%2C%20are%20still%20in%20the%20prototype%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacquier%20said%20such%20gameplay%20features%20are%20more%20experimental%20because%20studios%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20LLMs%2C%20for%20example%2C%20don't%20hallucinate.%20He%20said%20it's%20also%20important%20that%20the%20tech%20is%20fun%20and%20purposeful%2C%20not%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20expensive%20gadget%26quot%3B%20that%20no%20one%20cares%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20this%20experimental%20technology%20was%20a%20challenge%20for%20Jam%20and%20Tea%20Studios%20when%20making%20%26quot%3BRetail%20Mage.%26quot%3B%20The%20software%20and%20hardware%2C%20including%20cloud%20technology%20and%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20required%20to%20run%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-future-will-not-be-free-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20come%20with%20a%20high%20price%20tag.%20Farr%20said%20this%20is%20partially%20why%20there%20aren't%20many%20AI-native%20games%20on%20the%20market%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20nearly%20didn't%20do%20'Retail%20Mage'%20because%20we%20thought%20it%20was%20too%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20Farr%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20I%20couldn't%20build%20it.%20It's%20that%20it%20would%20have%20been%20too%20expensive%20to%20run.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aaron%20Farr%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20of%20Jam%20%26amp%3B%20Tea%20Studios%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68adc5b7194a2d49b8af2d0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAaron%20Farr%20is%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20of%20Jam%20%26amp%3B%20Tea%20Studios.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lutisha%20Aubrey%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b080a3ae-c3ff-4aa5-b65d-b10281b92a6d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsing%20AI%20responsibly%20is%20an%20ongoing%20conversation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20changes%20the%20way%20game%20makers%20and%20creatives%20work%2C%20studios%20are%20also%20navigating%20how%20to%20use%20the%20tech%20mindfully%20and%20responsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jacquier%2C%20this%20means%20examining%20the%20entire%20development%20process%20when%20adding%20in%20new%20technology.%20This%20big-picture%20approach%20is%20also%20helping%20his%20team%20find%20new%20ways%20to%20continue%20working%20with%20creative%20talent%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.