nd%20strengthening%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%20However%2C%20ensuring%20a%20steady%20group%20of%20committed%20volunteers%20is%20a%20challenge%20every%20season%2C%20making%20their%20presence%20even%20more%20invaluable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20they%20do%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20actual%20fieldwork%20begins%2C%20SSTCN%20must%20secure%20official%20approvals%20from%20the%20forest%20and%20police%20departments%20to%20commence%20the%20work%20in%20November.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20we%20start%20identifying%20who%20the%20walkers%20of%20the%20season%20are%20going%20to%20be%2C%20which%20is%20a%20difficult%20task%20and%20get%20ID%20cards%20for%20all%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20work%20begins%20on%201st%20January%20when%20volunteers%20start%20patrolling%20the%2014-kilometre%20stretch%20of%20beach%20every%20night.%20%E2%80%9CFour%20volunteers%2C%20two%20on%20this%20side%2C%20two%20on%20that%20side%2C%20will%20walk%20every%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun.%20They%20carefully%20search%20for%20turtle%20nests%2C%20collect%20eggs%2C%20and%20relocate%20them%20to%20the%20hatchery%2C%20ensuring%20the%20eggs%20are%20protected%20from%20predators%20and%20human%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20season%2C%20they%20often%20come%20across%20dead%20turtles%20that%20have%20washed%20ashore.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20finding%20a%20lot%20of%20dead%20turtles%2C%20but%20nothing%20like%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun.%20Volunteers%20mark%20these%20turtles%20and%20ensure%20they%20do%20not%20count%20the%20same%20ones%20twice.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20SSTCN%20also%20recorded%20the%20most%20nests%20this%20year%20than%20they%20ever%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Kartik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%20120