0more%20dedication%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteers%20monitor%20the%20hatchery%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20checking%20for%20emerging%20hatchlings%20every%20two%20hours.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20hatchlings%20are%20out%2C%20you%20also%20need%20to%20dig%20out%20and%20remove%20the%20rotten%20eggs%2C%20which%20is%20smelly%20work%20and%20not%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hatchlings%20are%20ready%2C%20they%20are%20released%20into%20the%20sea.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20we%20have%20had%20800%20to%201000%20people%20waiting%20to%20say%20bye%20to%20just%2010%20hatchlings%20on%20the%20beach%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20turtles%20have%20endured%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20dedication%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411878%2Folive-ridley-turtles-why-they-matter-balance-ecosystem-indicators%2F%5C%22%3Eprote%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411878%2Folive-ridley-turtles-why-they-matter-balance-ecosystem-indicators%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ec%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F411878%2Folive-ridley-turtles-why-they-matter-balance-ecosystem-indicators%2F%5C%22%3Eting%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20as%20easy%20or%20glamorous%20as%20it%20may%20seem.%20While%20poaching%20was%20once%20a%20major%20concern%2C%20stricter%20regulations%20have%20reduced%20its%20impact.%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20poaching%20is%20a%20minor%20threat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun.%20However%2C%20modern%20threats%20have%20emerged%2C%20making%20conservation%20efforts%20more%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArtificial%20lighting%20along%20the%20coast%20confuses%20hatchlings%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20head%20inland%20instead%20of%20towards%20the%20sea.%20This%20dehydrates%20the%20baby%20turtles