%2C%20to%20grow%20mushrooms.%20He%20informs%20that%20currently%202%2C000%20farmers%20are%20producing%20around%20600%20kg%20of%20mushrooms%20per%20day%2C%20whereas%205%2C000%20are%20reaping%20benefits%20by%20growing%20onions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prabhat%20says%20in%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20there%20is%20a%20one-time%20expense%20to%20procure%20the%20bags%20and%20get%20recurring%20income%20daily.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBihar-farmers-1-1715870697-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrabhat%20says%20in%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20there%20is%20a%20one-time%20expense%20to%20procure%20the%20bags%20and%20get%20a%20recurring%20income%20daily.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20mushrooms%2C%20Prabhat%20trained%20farmers%20to%20grow%20seed%20corn%2C%20baby%20corn%2C%20and%20strawberries%20which%20gave%20immediate%20results%20and%20better%20income.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20also%20set%20up%20Gaya%E2%80%99s%20largest%20processing%20unit%20with%20a%2010%2C000%20kg%20per%20day%20capacity%20to%20process%20crops%20to%20increase%20their%20she