ching%20our%20citizen-facing%20%E2%80%98Varuna%E2%80%99%20app%2C%20which%20will%20change%20citizens%20into%20frontline%20observers%20and%20responders.%20This%20will%20further%20strengthen%20trust%20and%20accelerate%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Sanitary%20Inspector%20DK%20Bironiya%20supports%20this%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20receive%20instant%20notifications%20from%20the%20Urban%20Flood%20Management%20Centre%20(UFMC)%20through%20WhatsApp%20messages%20or%20walkie-talkie-based%20transmissions%20whenever%20residents%20report%20complaints%20or%20waterlogging.%20This%20direct%20flow%20of%20information%20helps%20us%20to%20respond%20more%20quickly%20and%20efficiently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20dedicated%20grievance%20portal%2C%20community%20involvement%20has%20become%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20flood%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIntelligence%20at%20the%20core%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Early%20Warning%20System%20(EWS)%20plus%20Decision%20Support%20System%20(DSS)%20fuses%20multiple%20data%20sources%20%E2%80%94%20including%20weather%20forecasts%2C%20live%20rainfall%20data%2C%20water%20level%20sensor%20readings%2C%20drainage%20flow%20measurements%2C%20and%20historical%20flood%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20the%20EWS%20enables%20accurate%20rainfall%20forecasting%20and%20live%20water-level%20monitoring%2C%20supporting%20early%20pump%20activation%20and%20field%20deployment.%20In%20the%20long%20term%2C%20the%20DSS%20helps%20analyse%20structural%20weaknesses%20and%20identify%20priority%20zones%20for%20drainage%20improvement%2C%20flood%20barriers%2C%20and%20urban%20redesign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheshadri%20summarises%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20DSS%20acts%20as%20a%20strategic%20engine%3B%20it%20offers%20insight%20not%20just%20for%20managing%20floods%20but%20for%20rebuilding%20city%20infrastructure%20intelligently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%