ays%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20grow%20paddy%20on%20about%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%20The%20paddy%20we%20planted%20matured%20in%20120%20to%20130%20days%20and%20showed%20some%20improvement%20after%20using%20the%20fertiliser.%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sahu%20was%20selected%20for%20RKVY%20(Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana)-RAFTAAR%20that%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20the%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20sectors.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-1-1755836394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490454%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sahu%20was%20selected%20for%20RKVY%20(Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana)-RAFTAAR%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20strengthen%20the%20agriculture%20and%20allied%20sectors.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20economic%20benefits%20weren%E2%80%99t%20immediately%20apparent%2C%20we%20observed%20an%20increase%20in%20growth%20and%20grain%20kernel%20formation.%20We%20managed%20to%20harvest%20two%20to%20three%20quintals%20more%20paddy%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%20effort